spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:script: Validate('Select SDI DATA WIDTH as 80-bits when 12G-SDI STANDARD is selected', Not(And(Eq('RX_SDI_STD', '12G-SDI'), Neq('RX_SDI_DW', '80-bits'))));\ Validate('Select SDI DATA WIDTH as 40-bits when 6G-SDI STANDARD is selected', Not(And(Eq('RX_SDI_STD', '6G-SDI'), Neq('RX_SDI_DW', '40-bits'))));\ Validate('Select SDI DATA WIDTH as 20-bits when 3G-SDI and HD-SDI STANDARD is selected', Not(And(Eq('RX_SDI_STD', '3G-SDI and HD-SDI'), Neq('RX_SDI_DW', '20-bits'))));\

spirit:vendorExtensions.actel-cc:description: CoreUHD_SDIRX is a SDI Deframer. CoreUHD_SDIRX performs the deframing of the SDI data stream into raw video data.
